Suárez attending the 2017 Fénix Awards Cecilia Suárez is a Mexican actress. She has starred in over 60 films and television shows since 1997, being nominated for her acting on 15 occasions. She has received two lifetime achievement awards for her film and TV career: one in Mexico and one in Spain; in Mexico she was the first woman to receive such an award.[1] Suárez has had over 30 theatrical roles since 1992, with multiple awards and nominations.
